'''魯比克360'''（{{lang-en|Rubik's 360}}）是由[[扭計骰|扭計骰]]的發明人、[[匈牙利|匈牙利]]雕刻家、建築學教授[[厄爾諾·魯比克|厄爾諾·魯比克]]教授發明的一種[[三維空間|三維]]的智力玩具<ref>{{cite news|author=Alastair Jamieson|title=Rubik's Cube inventor is back with Rubik's 360|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/lifestyle/4412176/Rubiks-Cube-inventor-is-back-with-Rubiks-360.html|work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|date=2009-01-31|accessdate=2009-02-06|archive-date=2018-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180616031122/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/lifestyle/4412176/Rubiks-Cube-inventor-is-back-with-Rubiks-360.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。魯比克360於2009年2月5日在[[紐倫堡國際玩具展覽會|紐倫堡國際玩具展覽會]]首次亮相<ref name=TIME>{{cite news|author=William Lee Adams|title=The Rubik's Cube: A Puzzling Success|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1874509,00.html|work=[[Time_(magazine)|TIME]]|date=2009-01-28|accessdate=2009-02-06|archive-date=2013-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130826200145/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1874509,00.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，並提前在八月在全球上市。<ref name=TIME/>

魯比克360的玩法就是把內球體內的六個顏色球分別放到相同顏色的半球裡。不像原來的魔方，沒有公式要記，並與[[數學|數學]]沒有什麼關連，而偏向[[物理學|物理學]]方面。

像[[扭計骰|扭計骰]]，魯比克360-{只}-有一個解決辦法，但你不能打破它並解決它，它被認為是適合所有年齡。根據評論，魯比克360是非常令人上癮，引人入勝。<ref>{{cite web|author=Dan Harris|title=Rubik's 360: the first review|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/lifestyle/4412103/Rubiks-360-the-first-review.html|work=[[Sunday_Telegraph|Sunday Telegraph]]|date=2009-01-31|accessdate=2009-02-06|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130023952/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/lifestyle/4412103/Rubiks-360-the-first-review.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

